{
  "texts": [
    "Park et al. (2023) use hyperbolic neural networks and propose a Hyperbolic Affinity Learning method for spatial propagation and learning the hierarchical relationship among the pixels.",
    "Hyperbolic learning of graphs, text, and more.",
    "The advances in hyperbolic embeddings of hierarchies and the introduction of hyperbolic network layers have spurred research in several other research directions as well.",
    "As a logical extension of hierarchical embeddings, graph networks have been extended to hyperbolic space.",
    "Liu et al. (2019) and Chami et al. (2019) propose a tangent-based view to hyperbolic graph networks."
  ]
}